data.description: This charming single-family home in Cape Coral, FL has been lovingly occupied by only one family since it`s construction ensuring regular & well maintained upkeep. Stepping inside you will see a spacious interior with ample natural light, perfect for family gatherings & entertaining guests. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a warm & inviting atmosphere. Stepping outside you have a blank canvas to make this space truly your own. With ample space for a pool the possibilities are limitless. Home is conveniently located near schools. This home comes equipped with Solar Panels that are transferable. Schedule your private showing today, do not miss the opportunity to make this house your dream home!
